description:
//AAS- Arm and Sword

     A political division within Alpha Authority pushing for decisions regarding the better of Alpha Authority to be made.  By joining you show what you stand for, and that is the progression of Alpha Authority. 

//What is the gain?

     By joining you get to take part in our votes!  We vote for things as a whole and take it up to Zanziber himself.  We are the driving force of the Authority.  We are the people who are behind the scenes.

[NOTE]
     Post what political stance you wish to be on in the wall to be promoted, if you're independent and don't have a specific mindset you're already good to go!
     50 or more Independents to join your cause will allow you to get your own political party rank and it will be officially recognized.

